IRS990.ActivityOrMissionDesc: TO PROMOTE PROFESSIONALISM AMONG LAW ENFORCEMENT OFFICERS; TO INFLUENCE THE YOUTH OF FLORIDA IN AN EFFORT TO COMBAT DELINQUENCY; TO FURTHER POLICE-COMMUNITY RELATIONS BY INFORMING THE CITIZENS OF FLORIDA OF THE DAY-TO-DAY STRESS AND PROBLEMS OF THEIR LAW ENFORCEMENT OFFICERS; AND TO REPRESENT OFFICERS AND OTHER PUBLIC EMPLOYEES IN THE LEGAL, LABOR, LEGISLATIVE, AND POLITICAL MATTERS WHICH AFFECT THE LAW ENFORCEMENT PROFESSION, AND/OR THE INTERESTS AND WELL BEING OF OTHER PUBLIC EMPLOYEES.
